name: Premium company logos UI kit – Untitled UI
description:
We've spent hours tracking down and optimizing 100+ company logos to use as placeholders in your designs.


Every logo has been painstakingly optically sized proportionally to each other so they line up nicely in your website designs.


–––


Untitled UI is the largest Figma UI kit and design system in the world. Kickstart any project, save thousands of hours, and level up as a designer.


✨ Learn more and preview the full version at untitledui.com ✨


–––


All company logos are the property of their respective owners and included in this kit for educational purposes. Ask permission before using these logos in real projects.
